{"tid":2183510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黨媒truth hk又出fake news 又用721微博假圖","createTime":"2020-09-01T03:41:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T10:12:31.000Z","uid":119607,"like":50,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"de1562670f98de79bb401eb7d7355352187e3af5","tid":2183510,"uid":119607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:41:49.000Z","msg":"fake news hk 內容：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/haEM8OY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhaEM8OY.jpg&h=bc2554e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實721張假poster得親中共群組傳來傳去：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U2EdOPR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU2EdOPR.png&h=ae838de8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[img]<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/88cfhH7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F88cfhH7.jpg&h=5f948d64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9av8CH8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9av8CH8.png&h=e1f7dfd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yY1jKn9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyY1jKn9.png&h=b78b97ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[/img]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nlink比大家負評同report，重點屌出721 假poster，可以用埋英文講，入link暫停，負評：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oJomZZtkkrY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoJomZZtkkrY&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7vFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=bf8bc20e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oJomZZtkkrY</a>"},{"pid":"232e1faec93b4d96cf81444d03973355d1ff5b8c","tid":2183510,"uid":119607,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:45:28.000Z","msg":"報告公開後隨即惹來爭議，元朗區議員陳樹暉更指出，報告談及7.21元朗白衣人事件時，引用的一張「721得元朗、得天下」、召集民眾721當日到元朗聚集的文宣，早於721前已有網民發出澄清屬假圖。"},{"pid":"7493ca0781b582062614d39c6f4bf17b9f70a7ee","tid":2183510,"uid":119607,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:59:28.000Z","msg":"網民在721前澄清是假圖　報告無列明<br />\n<br />\n根據學生動源及連登資料，學生動源在7月19日已發出聲明，指上述圖片是假圖。而連登討論區在7月21日之前亦有網民發出澄清，指「721得元朗得天下」圖片是假圖。<br />\n<br />\n監警會報告並無引用「香港人721遍地開花」的假圖，但就引用了「721得元朗得天下」的圖片，但引用時並無列明這是假圖及事發前已有人澄清。"},{"pid":"3b97e7f1f0c8fd1f5718acfccb2fcfebca689489","tid":2183510,"uid":54593,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:01:37.000Z","msg":"自編自導"},{"pid":"ee0e269b5a82142270f156a650dbf446265ed74a","tid":2183510,"uid":119607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:11:18.000Z","msg":"stop play，之後負評。"},{"pid":"f40df2bd2aacf377e506230b41e4b12bb9ad9726","tid":2183510,"uid":39710,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:12:04.000Z","msg":"垃圾媒體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb62399ec92a970a0c51d926e0f3adcfcece358","tid":2183510,"uid":34789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:14:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a91356e895758e4152611ec5ff588398dc1e934f","tid":2183510,"uid":119607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f40df2bd2aacf377e506230b41e4b12bb9ad9726","tid":2183510,"uid":39710,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:12:04.000Z","msg":"垃圾媒體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:16:39.000Z","msg":"黨媒不嬲垃圾。"},{"pid":"ea2cb98d151b4f064a1c994bbab5b7fb25e53761","tid":2183510,"uid":34789,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T04:19:30.000Z","msg":"有人整假圖721 fake人去元朗, 請廣傳並幫手澄清<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1330298\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1330298</a><br />\n<br />\n出面流傳緊假文宣，叫人721去元朗<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1331152\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1331152</a><br />\n<br />\n元朗真係唔建議大家搞光復<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1324612\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1324612</a><br />\n<br />\n當我